frames.caption: A woman in a white floral dress and hijab sits comfortably on an outdoor sofa in a vast savannah. Beside her, a majestic lion stands, gazing into the distance.
frames.description: The scene is set in an open savannah, featuring a tranquil interaction between a woman and a lion. The woman appears relaxed and content, while the lion adds an element of wildness and majesty to the setting.

frames.caption: A woman in a light-colored hijab sits calmly on a chair in an open savannah, while a majestic lion walks closely beside her. The scene captures a serene interaction between human and nature under the soft, golden light of the setting sun.
frames.description: The image depicts a tranquil moment in a savannah setting, where a woman is seated comfortably outdoors, accompanied by a lion. The vast, open landscape and the gentle interaction create a peaceful and harmonious atmosphere.
